Package util

Class SortedMediaList

java.lang.Object
util.SortedMediaList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Media>
public class SortedMediaList extends Object implements Iterable<Media>
List for storing Media objects in a sorted order, modeled after a LinkedList. Does not allow duplicates.
Author:
Hunter Pruitt
